112
00:11:32.501 --> 00:11:33.801
<v Daniel>There's no curtain to hide behind.</v>

113
00:11:34.021 --> 00:11:40.424
<v Maya>Exactly. The entire process from walking in to the consultation to the procedure happens above the line of visibility.</v>

114
00:11:40.842 --> 00:11:45.728
<v Daniel>So how do you blueprint an experience when you can't hide the messy support processes?</v>

115
00:11:45.969 --> 00:11:55.140
