117
00:11:56.567 --> 00:12:07.393
<v Maya>Like the specific moments a nurse needs to show empathy or ask a sensitive question. And they linked those to physical things like the sterility of the equipment or handing over a specific pamphlet.</v>

118
00:12:07.453 --> 00:12:12.215
<v Daniel>Wow, so the blueprint dictated exactly what needed to be in the room and what needed to be said.</v>

119
00:12:12.475 --> 00:12:16.657
