129
00:13:10.678 --> 00:13:13.700
<v Maya>The blueprint visualized the customer's physical pain.</v>

130
00:13:14.080 --> 00:13:17.703
<v Daniel>They drew a map of exhaustion, and then they engineered it out of existence.</v>

131
00:13:18.003 --> 00:13:25.128
